"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-04-Tribute-to-excellence-Celebrating-the-Olympic-spirit-through-art-1vN2PeIwvjG-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  CGTN  Copied  An exhibition showcasing representative paintings of German artist Rolf Lukaschewski is held at the Beijing Olympic Museum to pay tribute to the Olympic Games. /CFP  An exhibition showcasing representative paintings of German artist Rolf Lukaschewski is held at the Beijing Olympic Museum to pay tribute to the Olympic Games. /CFP  An exhibition showcasing representative paintings of German artist Rolf Lukaschewski is held at the Beijing Olympic Museum to pay tribute to the Olympic Games. /CFP  An exhibition showcasing representative paintings of German artist Rolf Lukaschewski is held at the Beijing Olympic Museum to pay tribute to the Olympic Games. /CFP  An exhibition showcasing representative paintings of German artist Rolf Lukaschewski is held at the Beijing Olympic Museum to pay tribute to the Olympic Games. /CFP  As athletes from around the world compete at the Summer Olympics in Paris, an Olympic-themed painting exhibition is being held at the Beijing Olympic Museum to honor both the summer and winter editions of the Olympic Games. The exhibition, named \\\"Tribute to Excellence: Olympians from Ancient Greece to Modern Times,\\\" showcases representative paintings of German artist Rolf Lukaschewski. The artworks convey his interpretation of the Olympic movement and the enduring legacy of the Olympic spirit, highlighting ancient Olympic sports and athletes from the Summer and Winter Olympics.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"